## Introduction

Hey, and welcome to my little home in geminispace. Here's where I'll be hosting some stuff aimed at being read via `gemini://`.

If you want to find me in the other place, the best place to start is:

=> https://davep.at/

Other places you'll find me in Geminispace:

=> gemini://bbs.geminispace.org/u/davep
=> gemini://station.martinrue.com/davep

## Software

### Rogallo

I am currently having a lot of fun developing Rogallo, my Gemini client for the terminal. The site for it is here:

=> https://rogallo.davep.dev/ Rogallo on the web
=> rogallo/index.gmi Rogallo

### Gemtext

In support of the work on Rogallo, I've written a small Python library for parsing Gemtext content.

=> https://gemtext.davep.dev/ Gemtext on the web
=> gemtext/index.gmi Gemtext

### Wasat

In support of the work on Rogallo, I've developed a Python library that provides an async client for the Gemini protocol.

=> https://wasat.davep.dev/ Wasat on the web
=> wasat/index.gmi Wasat
